reviewText: Our kids love these and we also find ourselves laughing and sing along with slugs and bugs, can't say that about any other children's songs we've ever owned. The videos are clever and fun. Buy it!

The grandkids love this music and video but I have ordered 3 of these and 2 of the 3 DVD's don't work!!  The first video plays then the DVD goes back to the beginning again.  I am returning this DVD and will try to find a copy that works.
Have not been able to get the video to play. Plays the first selection over and over.
The music is outstanding. Nothing else like it out there! My favorite video to put on for the kids!
